title: Blank App Designer Cordova Template
tooltip: Use this template to develop a cross-platform mobile app using the drag-and-drop App Designer UI editor and your choice of UI widgets provided by Intel App Framework, jQuery Mobile, Bootstrap or Topcoat. Apps developed with this template can be built to run on various mobile devices.
